{"tid":1161940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支媒靜音！支那今日再傳軍機墜毀 場面怵目","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T14:17:30.000Z","uid":32511,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a4ccca889d36f9f3833f38c559fd67f53e88ca","tid":1161940,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"微博這兩天流傳一段疑似軍機墜毀的影片，場面驚心怵目。但中國官方卻未證實此事；上月中國才有飛行員在飛行任務中迫降身亡，今又傳此憾事，引起不少網友議論紛紛。<br />\n <br />\n 中國昨天再傳疑似軍機墜毀的影片，在一處高樓建築旁爆炸湧現一團火球。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G0kfqTveC2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG0kfqTveC2s&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a61c03c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G0kfqTveC2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpuxMjd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpuxMjd1.jpg&h=6f52a685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有中媒報導，網友分享這段錄影畫面昨天在微博上還看得到，據說是昨（18）日上午7時17分發生在山東省威海市。影片中可見一飛行物突然從畫面上方幾乎筆直急速墜地，接著在一棟高樓旁爆炸，駭人火球瞬間往空中竄。還有民眾拍到現場殘骸，並有一名身穿中共解放軍裝的人員查看落在建築旁的降落傘，網友猜測，飛行員在飛機墜毀爆炸前可能已順利逃生。<br />\n <br />\n中媒指稱，該架墜毀軍機疑似是殲轟-7A戰鬥轟炸機。<br />\n <br />\n中共官方日前才證實，上月26日「特級飛行員」查顯偉在執行一項飛行任務時，因突發機械故障只得迫降，最後不幸隨軍機墜毀罹難。相隔不到一個月又傳軍機墜毀，目前官方媒體尚未有相關消息，解放軍也未出面證實。"},{"pid":"8c449f8a99eda0fdfdaa23c4c4c2f326f5c7e343","tid":1161940,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:54:27.000Z","msg":"用国產為国捐驅是光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d760124450cdde7b75fff77a5a3055adee17486","tid":1161940,"uid":130105,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"連墮機勁過美國喎，贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e17b6a086fdd1eb93e39f7a8d123a5c0a03f222","tid":1161940,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"銀牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5215548b9d0f451d24460970aa7011a206a48442","tid":1161940,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"其實係咪用錯咗導彈既設計，落咗戰機度？"},{"pid":"060e5c5ecda520944477d39cb87ffe23997253dc","tid":1161940,"uid":69994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"膽敢洩露國家機密 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57b7f6eb60bb3ae4d36621d312caa806ebd234e","tid":1161940,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef8b5d98fd324f69f8616ef7525372cd1fa7e6e","tid":1161940,"uid":215905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁撚廢 無壓力下都咁"},{"pid":"dbd6023f870755b39d6eddb92cb8e1b2d7b6ac01","tid":1161940,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"肯定係美國戰機啦"},{"pid":"d2a4f5cdc42d6f95aa7cd8e04b1a3440bd4a34fc","tid":1161940,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"未開戰已經無曬飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed97e34e097fc48f3329e1096ddece8ca0fb6b0","tid":1161940,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"留